  /*                                                                       */
  /* <Description>                                                         */
  /*    Blits a bitmap from an input stream into a given target.  Supports */
  /*    x and y offsets as well as byte padded lines.                      */
  /*                                                                       */
  /* <Input>                                                               */
  /*    target      :: The target bitmap/pixmap.                           */
  /*                                                                       */
  /*    source      :: The input packed bitmap data.                       */
  /*                                                                       */
